@startuml
title Figure 1: System Architecture - VJTI Launchpad
actor "User (Browser)" as User
rectangle "React SPA\n(Vite + Redux)" as SPA
rectangle "REST API\nNode.js + Express" as API
database "MongoDB\n(Mongoose)" as DB
cloud "Cloudinary\n(Assets)" as Cloud

User --> SPA : Interacts (UI)
SPA --> API : HTTPS REST (withCredentials)
API --> DB : CRUD (Mongoose)
API --> Cloud : Upload files (Cloudinary SDK)

note right of API
 Authentication: JWT in cookie
 Routes: /api/v1/user, /company, /job, /application
end note
@enduml
